title: Gross National Product, Income Estimates for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1939-1945 (2)--Seasonally Adjusted Data, 1946-1966. The Data Represent Gross National Product In Current Dollars Minus "Statistical Discrepancy" Source: Survey Of Current Business, August 1965 And Subsequent Issues.

This NBER data series q08280b appears on the NBER website in Chapter 8 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter08.html.
